Description: Tree-based Scan Statistics are an explorative method to identify
             event clusters across the space of a hirachical tree. This package
             implements the unconditional Bernoulli Scan Statitic developed by
             Kulldorff et al. (2003) <doi:10.1111/1541-0420.00039> 
             for hirachical tree structures.
